      "kind": "tip",
      "title": "Identifying S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 & Pr\u00edncipe",
      "items": [
        {
          "kind": "centeredImage",
          "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/0_st_summary.png"
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_shit.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/LTkTMgjD7rxFCcgE8",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "All the coverage was taken with a low quality camera that\u2019s commonly referred to as \u201cShitcam\u201d. The car will often be completely blurred, with a **very large blur** covering the back and a [somewhat smaller blur](https://goo.gl/maps/YfaEf11wuzdt3NYv8) covering the front.",
              "NOTE: The coverage is a newer variant of shitcam, where the image is dimmer and hazier than the original shitcam primarily found in [India](https://maps.app.goo.gl/3MYW94icKvwhWTc66) and [Nigeria](https://maps.app.goo.gl/eETqUgMHvyiCR4di8)."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_language.png",
              "imageLink": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_language.png",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "**Portuguese** is the main language used on S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_polepedestriancrossing.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/4ojwFdj6pSKUkbeF8",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "On top of the language, the Portuguese influence can also be seen in infrastructure, such as ladder poles and pedestrian signs with the same design as in Portugal."
            ]
          },
          "tags": [
            "pole"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_tropical.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/qjvx6rFCZPN7M3QdA",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "S\u00e3o Tom\u00e9 and Pr\u00edncipe are **tropical islands**, which are almost completely covered in rainforests. Banana plants are especially common throughout the islands."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/antenna.png",
              "imageLink": "https://maps.app.goo.gl/4VeKVBatyNNenp8y9",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "In many locations, you will notice a **slanted antenna** protruding from the side of the car."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/st_bluepolepaint.png",
              "imageLink": "https://goo.gl/maps/6x7TkiEeH4v4XSGL7",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Some wooden poles are painted **blue **on the bottom. You can also read the letters **CST **on them."
            ]
          },
          "tags": [
            "pole"
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "tip",
          "data": {
            "image": {
              "imageUrl": "/images/sao-tome-and-principe/yellow_taxi_sao_tome.png",
              "imageLink": "https://maps.app.goo.gl/JkNYuG5P1kwrHWMa8",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 0.5
            },
            "text": [
              "Taxis and minibuses are painted in a **bright yellow** colour."
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
